summary: This code defines a class `AITransferModel` that conforms to the NSCoding protocol, allowing it to be encoded and decoded using NSKeyedArchiver and NSKeyedUnarchiver. It provides an initializer method `newWithScene:canset:` for creating instances of this class with specified scene and canset values. The code also includes implementations of the required NSCoding methods, `initWithCoder:` for decoding object properties from a coder and `encodeWithCoder:` for encoding object properties to a coder.
